  "description": "<p>Tabular dataset (6,607 records; 20 variables) for student performance analytics. Includes demographics and learning-context factors and the outcome <strong>Exam_Score</strong>. Intended for regression, uncertainty estimation, and budgeted Top-K screening / governance routing experiments. Missing values occur only in three categorical fields (Teacher_Quality, Parental_Education_Level, Distance_from_Home).</p>",
